dc_description_s: This data layer represents zoning for Walworth County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Walworth_Zoning_2018.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Walworth_General_2018' and 'Walworth_Shoreland_2018'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data for this county, please visit: https://open-walco.opendata.arcgis.com/
